snippet.title: Fatal Frame II: Crimson Butterfly Director's Cut (Xbox longplay)
snippet.description:
Horror games generally aren't my thing but I do love the creepy atmosphere in this game. It's been a while since I've gone through it so I suck at fighting ghosts to begin with. I'm replaying this on the PS2 where i'm finding it much easier knowing the patterns of the ghosts.

I've included all the xbox endings at the end of the video. The first one is the default ending.
